OL,3,CRoyal Navy seizes almost #33m worth of
OL,4,Cdrugs in Indian Ocean
OL,6,FThe Royal Navy has seized nearly #33m
OL,7,Fworth of illegal drugs from
OL,8,Ftraffickers in the Middle East.
OL,10,FAcross two operations in less than 24
OL,11,Fhours, HMS Lancaster seized a total of
OL,12,F3.7 tonnes of illegal drugs including
OL,13,Fheroin, crystal meth and cannabis from
OL,14,Fsmugglers in the Indian Ocean.
OL,16,FDefence Secretary Grant Shapps said
OL,17,Fthe actions of the crews dealt a
OL,18,F"decisive blow to criminal networks".
