OL,3,CRoyal Navy seizes almost #33m worth of
OL,4,Cdrugs in Indian Ocean
OL,6,FThe ship was on its first security
OL,7,Fpatrol following a training period
OL,8,Fwhen its Wildcat helicopter spotted a
OL,9,Fsuspicious vessel.
OL,11,FThe first operation lasted eight hours
OL,12,Fduring which Royal Marines from 42
OL,13,FCommando secured the boat, allowing
OL,14,FLancaster's sailors to board the
OL,15,Fvessel and recover nearly 100 packages
OL,16,Fcontaining heroin and crystal meth.
