OL,3,CRoyal Navy seizes almost #33m worth of
OL,4,Cdrugs in Indian Ocean
OL,6,FLess than 24 hours later, commandos
OL,7,Fand sailors from the Lancaster seized
OL,8,F2.4 tonnes of hashish, a form of
OL,9,Fcannabis, after the Royal Navy ship
OL,10,Fworked with its helicopter to spot and
OL,11,Ftrack another suspected boat
OL,12,Fthroughout the night.
OL,14,FCollectively, the drugs seized in both
OL,15,Foperations had a street value of just
OL,16,Funder #33m, according to the National
OL,17,FCrime Agency.
OL,19,FThis comes just weeks after #17
OL,20,Fmillion worth of illegal narcotics was
OL,21,Fsized by HMS Trent in the Caribbean.
