OL,3,CRoyal Navy seizes almost #33m worth of
OL,4,Cdrugs in Indian Ocean
OL,6,FMr Shapps said: "The fantastic
OL,7,Fachievements of the crew of HMS
OL,8,FLancaster and Royal Marine commandos
OL,9,Fin the Indian Ocean shows the
OL,10,Fimportant role our Navy plays policing
OL,11,Fthe oceans.
OL,13,F"Their relentless effort and
OL,14,Fprofessionalism have dealt another
OL,15,Fdecisive blow to criminal networks."
OL,17,FCommanding officer Chris Sharp said:
OL,18,F"I am exceptionally proud of the
OL,19,Fentire team in Lancaster executing
OL,20,Fthese two interdictions on the first
OL,21,Ftwo days of our deployment.
